++++## CI-Equivalent Definition of Done (Required)
++++
++++All work must be в•¬Гҙв”ңв–“в”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“Г¶Гұв•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬ГәО“Г¶ВЈв”¬в•‘в•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“ГІГҰCI-equivalent greenв•¬Гҙв”ңв–“в”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“Г¶Гұв•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬ГәО“Г¶ВЈв”¬в•‘в•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈв”ңВӘ before requesting a review or opening/refreshing a PR. This means you must run the same checks CI runs, in this order, and log the commands + outputs in `merge-notes.md`:
++++
++++1) Policy validation (must pass first):
++++- `pnpm ci:validate`
++++
++++2) Quality gates:
++++- `pnpm lint`
++++- `pnpm typecheck`
++++- `pnpm test`
++++- `pnpm build` (run locally unless explicitly excluded for a documented reason)
++++
++++If any command fails, you must fix the issue and rerun the full suite until all are green.
++++
++++Patch artifacts are part of в•¬Гҙв”ңв–“в”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“Г¶Гұв•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬ГәО“Г¶ВЈв”¬в•‘в•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“ГІГҰdoneв•¬Гҙв”ңв–“в”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈО“Г¶Гұв•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬ГәО“Г¶ВЈв”¬в•‘в•¬Гҙв”ңв•ўв”¬в•қО“Г¶ВЈв”ңВӘ and must reflect the current diff. Before generating patches, run `git add -N .` so new files are included in diffs. Then regenerate both artifacts and record `ls -lh` outputs in `merge-notes.md`:
++++- `artifacts/day-<N>.patch` (cumulative: `develop...HEAD`)
++++- `artifacts/day-<N>-this-run.patch` (incremental: current run)
++++
++++Required deliverables must be present AND tracked (not left untracked), including:
++++- `docs/change-briefs/day-<N>.md`
++++- `merge-notes.md` (and archived prior day notes under `docs/merge-notes/` when starting a new day)
++++
++++Do not commit or push. Provide text-only suggested commit message/PR title in merge-notes, but never execute git commit/push steps.
++++
